message: Probably the best game of the entire GSTL, though funniest goes to the one before it (ST_Bomber vs IMLosira)
Epic swings, and you can listen to Artosis go through a second puberty.
I take it back, ST_Squirtle vs IMMvp best game of GSTL.
I'm really loving the new maps too.
I was so impressed with that match. MVP is so quick to figure out what he needs to do to stay relevant and ahead of his opponent.
